description: Sophistication and style blend to create a wonderful loft-style home at Court Square Press! This open concept 2 bedroom, 2 full bathroom home has a great layout with plenty of space to entertain as well as ample storage. Upon entering the space, one is immediately struck by the high ceilings accented by the original elements of this antique mill with beautiful wood-beamed ceilings and columns as well as large windows and red brick walls. The main living space has a wonderful kitchen featuring a large stone peninsula for prep work, plenty of cabinetry and a pantry for extra storage. Flanking the main living space are two king-size en-suite bedrooms both of which have large walk-in closets and full baths. Both bathrooms have large, granite-topped vanities, white subway tile, and white cast iron tubs. Many upgrades, including replacing the entire heating and cooling systems, a newer Viking fridge and gas range, Lutron lights, and voice-activated smart home technology.  Don't miss out!
